# ------------------------------------------------------------
#
#  Regex: SVG Path-Splitting
#  	Designed to simplify SVG modification
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------

### Find Regex:

((?:[aAcChHlLmMqQsSvV] ?(?:[0-9e,-\.]+ )+(?=[aAcChHlLmMqQsSvVzZ]))+)([Zz]) ?


### Replace with:

\n$1$2\n


